dict.acceptation: 保护，保卫；贸易保护；备款以支付；

sent.orig: Because desert wind is big ah, can protect our eye! Can protect our eye!
sent.trans: 因为沙漠风沙大呀，可以保护我们的眼睛呀！

sent.orig: We have walls around our property to protect us, they have friends to protect them.
sent.trans: 我们的财产由高墙守护，他们的生命有朋友捍卫。

sent.orig: The Protect Polymer MCS helps protect essential lipids, prevents moisture loss and restores colour treated hair.
sent.trans: 仙姬造型产品的配方含高份子保护膜MCS,防止头发脂质及水份流失，减少染发后色泽褪色。

sent.orig: Governments protect goods and capital largely in order to protect jobs.
sent.trans: 各国政府对信贷与商品的保护主要是为了保护就业岗位。

sent.orig: Doctors think it also help to protect protect against infection infections.
sent.trans: 医生认为耳蜡还能防止感染。
